description:
In this edition of Tequila SunGeist, Jack and super producer Becca discuss Trump and family getting sued in NY, Putin threatening to end the world, Brad Pitt's skincare line, Aaron Judge fever, the search for a new Bond, Tom Hardy's martial arts tournament victory, and Becca's TikTok Corner!
